_sText:
You may get a message telling you that the navigation mesh was built using a different version of the map. That is because I changed the sky type. That is all. The bots should work fine.

This is my 3rd map and 2nd release, I hope you enjoy it. Please provide constructive criticism, as I wish to improve upon my map making skills. 

**Beta Version** Please report any known bugs or improvements to be made
